        public static Layer getConvLayer(int numFilters,
                                 int filterSize,
                                 int stride,
                                 java.lang.String activation,
                                 int numberOfNeuronsToLayer)
        Creates and sets up an instance of LayerConvolution.
        Parameters:
        numFilters - The number of neurons for this layer.
        filterSize - The size of the receptive field.
        stride - The stride that this layer will use.
        activation - The LayerActivation type that this layer will use.
        numberOfNeuronsToLayer - The number of inputs channels to the layer.
        Returns:
        An instance of LayerConvolution.
